@startuml State Diagram - Payment Lifecycle
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam StateBorderColor #4A90D9
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #EBF4FF
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

title State Diagram — Payment Lifecycle

[*] --> PAYMENT_PAGE : Customer clicks Pay Now

PAYMENT_PAGE --> PROCESSING : Customer selects method\nand submits

PROCESSING --> SUCCESS : PaymentProcessor returns\n"SUCCESS"
PROCESSING --> FAILED : PaymentProcessor returns\n"FAILED"

SUCCESS --> [*] : Order confirmed,\ntracking initiated
FAILED --> PAYMENT_PAGE : Customer retries

PROCESSING : do / PaymentFactory.getProcessor(method)\ndo / processor.processPayment(orderId, amount)
SUCCESS : entry / Update order status → CONFIRMED\nentry / Add tracking steps
FAILED : entry / Save payment record (FAILED)

@enduml
